{"about_the_game":"Dive into the heart-pounding action of<strong><strong> Zombie Island,</strong></strong> an adrenaline-fueled survival game that will push your skills to the limit! Are you ready to face hordes of ravenous undead in a battle for survival?<br><br>In Zombie Island, you'll find yourself stranded on a desolate island infested with the walking dead. Armed with only your wits and a selection of powerful weapons, you must fight your way through wave after wave of zombies, each more relentless than the last.<br><br>But beware \u2013 these zombies aren't your average shufflers. With our cutting-edge 3D audio technology, you'll hear every groan, every footstep, and every bone-chilling growl as the undead close in from all directions. Stay alert, or risk becoming zombie chow!<br><br>But be warned: surviving on Zombie Island won't be easy. With each passing wave, the challenges will escalate, testing your reflexes, strategy, and nerve. Do you have what it takes to outlast the undead and emerge victorious?<br><br>Prepare yourself for the ultimate test of survival. Gather your courage, lock and load your weapons, and get ready to face the zombie apocalypse head-on in Zombie Island \u2013 where every shot counts, and every scream could be your last.<br><br>Join us now on Steam and prepare to experience the thrill of Zombie Island firsthand. The undead await \u2013 are you brave enough to face them?","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733980345","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925210/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733980345","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925210/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733980345","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925210/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733980345","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_d